import type { FontSizeRamp } from '../../system'

/* eslint-disable sort-keys-fix/sort-keys-fix */
export const fontSizes: FontSizeRamp = {
  xxxxxlarge: '2.75rem',
  xxxxlarge: '2.25rem',
  xxxlarge: '1.75rem',
  xxlarge: '1.5rem',
  xlarge: '1.375rem',
  large: '1.125rem',
  medium: '1rem',
  small: '0.875rem',
  xsmall: '0.75rem',
  xxsmall: '0.6875rem',
}
/* eslint-enable sort-keys */
